Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.50,0:00:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們繼續去找鷹之團了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.93,0:00:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.41,0:00:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 為什麼敢來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.71,0:00:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什... ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.82,0:00:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.64,0:01:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼 還不殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.81,0:01:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箭一支都沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然躲開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼多的數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.95,0:01:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨 發什麼呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.75,0:01:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二波 放箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.79,0:01:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.47,0:03:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個男人的同夥嗎 把這傢伙幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個劍士怎麼回事 是怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持住敵人 只有兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點捉住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 敵陣前不能下馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.80,0:03:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫勞古斯 按照神諭的指引來此參戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.39,0:03:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必你就是光之鷹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.01,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月光騎士洛克斯 你的劍我收下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.77,0:03:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬心喜悅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.07,0:04:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我在溫達姆城凱旋避行中見過 肯定是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人才是米特蘭的守護神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.08,0:04:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等 危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.93,0:04:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風在耳語著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.51,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在世界要闊始改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止他們 阻止那兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.73,0:04:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顧及這些傢伙的生死有什麼好處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先趁著混亂 把鷹抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.33,0:04:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上竟有如此美麗的人 美得不像人類一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.63,0:05:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 竟然把我們擊飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢 遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為巴基拉卡的頂尖的達巴沙叫人失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個面具 你是拉克沙斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,族中的流放者為何在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.86,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽預言說 你就是光之鷹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.25,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 我要割下你的頭顱 讓它屬於我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前我不會讓別人傷害你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你們倆玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關上城門 斷絶他們的退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人 龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.79,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別退縮 敵人只有一個上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳令 要塞裡的人全部出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.78,0:06:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撲鼻的味道 瀰漫著的血腥味讓腦袋裡都麻木了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.62,0:07:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都染紅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.42,0:07:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕陽的照射下 全都一片血紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如此慘絶人寰的景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.89,0:07:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但那是世上絶無僅有的一幅圖畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.35,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在確確實實就在這駭人聽聞的故事當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您讓我們加入您的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你還不快跪下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可疑了 突然改變態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.39,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是想鑽空子抓我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.89,0:08:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經捨棄教籍還俗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.06,0:08:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能相信你們這幫貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.11,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道 超越了我所深信的秩序的真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.07,0:08:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想學習 能在沒有秩序的黑暗中生存的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請指引我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用難懂的話矇混過去可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.76,0:08:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們對喀絲卡大姐做的事該怎解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.10,0:08:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點就被火燒了要想讓昨日的敵人變成朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.61,0:08:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來給大爺跪一下吧 做得到嗎 自傲的貴族們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打嗎 來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.46,0:09:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能做這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚有一天會謝罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要再得寸進尺的話就是真正的反派了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.93,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺和貴族小姐都那麼誇張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.10,0:09:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你們的便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好乾脆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交代和道歉都不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也幹掉了你們的同伴 彼此彼此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是指引就算了 我不適合那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.36,0:09:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你想知道什麼隨便做就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不礙我的事 我也不會說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.95,0:09:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.41,0:09:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說這個還早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.63,0:09:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們一起走 就意味著能睡覺的夜晚不會再來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會有幽靈 怪物出現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.55,0:10:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點奇怪 那個格斯竟然這麼會乾脆的接受別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.98,0:10:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人的話 以前的我一定會不由分說拒絶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說貫話這次真是難辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.41,0:10:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然第一次這麼期待別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是你在指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為自己的不詳而戰傈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被自己的無力所打垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她最後一次歡笑是什麼時候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是對王室盡忠也不是為了貴族的臉面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是為了拯救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的領民們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 米特蘭人的俘虜嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 全軍齊射 放箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己人也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用箭瞄準嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎兵突擊 全殲他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.65,0:11:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.12,0:11:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右翼有新敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左翼也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們至底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.69,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個旗幟是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一道白光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.72,0:12:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直指敵人意志的中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.06,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛 飛起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡真的是戰場嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼祥和的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到是被異國軍隊蹂躪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是古力菲斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位白鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為有古力菲斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才能露出笑臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.46,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位少女是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道讀了我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到鷹之團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士氣多麼高漲的士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.18,0:14:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是庫夏人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.02,0:14:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼敵人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題一個一個問啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.77,0:14:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是順從者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這異樣的壓迫感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.66,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我軍的規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.74,0:14:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虜要三次上場衝鋒之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.45,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下來的可以選擇歸降或者自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順從者們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.42,0:14:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據之後的表現可以和普通士兵一樣得到晉升機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據情況還能領兵打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這太胡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把士兵訐付給敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏人也不是一塊磐石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.93,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疋一個王族打敗不同的部族後才獲得帝位的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.61,0:15:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡面有很多深仇大恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們米特蘭人的感受怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.74,0:15:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街道 家庭 父母兄弟被殺的人的怨恨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.87,0:15:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說各有怨恨但大家都是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.12,0:15:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這要待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.17,0:15:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能明白往日的敵人更容易變得親近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個騎士是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.42,0:15:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是洛克斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責鷹之團的新兵訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是那個月光騎士洛克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然嚇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.56,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,習武之人都這一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在無數戰場上立下武勛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御前比武和決鬥沒有敗績的榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.73,0:15:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絶不跟從一位主人 歷至今的最強騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位活生生的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你還會更加吃驚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比洛克斯大人說的庫夏人還要吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊是近路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.47,0:16:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼在這個森林裡盤踞著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.27,0:16:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,異常的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野獸 還是狼群嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.82,0:16:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也在白天的戰鬥中大顯身手了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家稱之為戰魔兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰魔兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣還算好很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前還吃過庫夏人的俘虜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.72,0:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.80,0:17:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又一個人來這裡了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.47,0:17:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧了趕緊放我下來 色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好就沒吃過人類的肉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和古力菲斯大人去告狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個千萬不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古倫貝路多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人是我們主人的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.13,0:17:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出手的話我來做你對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的 只是開個玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古倫貝路多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從大國蕕塔的進攻中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.35,0:17:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在北方小國僅憑自己率領的三千兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅守十年的巨人豪傑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之巨龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說他應該戰死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索妮亞 你也太不小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是鷹的巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能一個人不帶就來這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.37,0:18:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要來的時候和我打聲招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.25,0:18:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹之巫女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.67,0:18:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚詳情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的非人軍團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.14,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名震世界的英雄們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.77,0:18:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帝古力菲斯大人的客人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.16,0:18:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天死在戰場上的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥結柬之後會變成幽靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣聚集起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.92,0:19:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰死者的血親或者戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來進行最後道別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.19,0:19:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.86,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.75,0:19:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.77,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索妮亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算什麼大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.07,0:20:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和古力菲斯大人在一起我的力量也變強了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.87,0:20:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色的鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.91,0:20:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群光到底要去向何處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為一體之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為一體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天國 還是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總有一天會明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒個人都會有那麼一天的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很榮幸見到你 苗路殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是古力菲斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個鷹之團的團長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.52,0:20:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多有失敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.82,0:20:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是苗路·禾夫拉姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是盧米阿斯領主巴拉格·沃夫拉姆的末子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在剛才的戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的臣下領民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從危機之中解救真的十分感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.46,0:20:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才是要道謝的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.92,0:21:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們提供的糧草夠我們支持幾個月的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您過獎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.59,0:21:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.72,0:21:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在胸囗不斷涌動的強烈感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湧現出的 這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.61,0:21:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您收下這把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.70,0:21:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對剛見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只說過一句話的這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.71,0:21:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的內心深處這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.88,0:21:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.63,0:21:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強而有力的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遒就是 命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.73,0:23:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了 伊斯多洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.07,0:23:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.07,0:23:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露大人 請保證火不要熄滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.16,0:23:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.95,0:23:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.99,0:23:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼擅自行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.54,0:23:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.25,0:23:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放馬過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.59,0:23:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些土左衛門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.46,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.40,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼解決啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.94,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,大家把柴火聚集起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.50,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,柴火要保持整夜不滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.53,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,放開那女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.10,0:24:06.19,Preview,,0,0,0,,那是因為你抱住了奇怪的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.15,0:24:10.23,Preview,,0,0,0,,啊 我最好的衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.36,0:24:14.53,Preview,,0,0,0,,這是魔法的儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.61,0:24:18.70,Preview,,0,0,0,,你就是這樣一路走來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.74,0:24:22.70,Preview,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到靈樹之館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.80,0:01:40.32,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur3.5\pos(1000,770)}飛劍的戰旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.12,0:24:28.21,Title,,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord0\shad0\pos(972,800)\fs95}獸鬼的森林
